sql:
SELECT category_name
FROM aqi_categories
WHERE category_name IN ('Unhealthy for sensitive groups', 'Unhealthy', 'Very unhealthy', 'Hazardous');

external_knowledge:
- 'worst air quality' refers to the highest average AQI values; 
- 'last year' refers to the year 2023;
- Air Quality Index (AQI) is a measure of how polluted the air currently is or how polluted it is forecasted to become; 
- A higher AQI value indicates poorer air quality.

